org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.api

Interface QueryBuilder<T,R extends QueryBuilder<T,R>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the data type
    R - the type of the builder so that extensions of this builder can maintain type
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseQueryBuilder<T,Query<T>,R>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    VectorQueryBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    QueryBuilderImpl, VectorQueryBuilderImpl

    public interface QueryBuilder<T,R extends QueryBuilder<T,R>>
extends BaseQueryBuilder<T,Query<T>,R>
    A QueryBuilder can be used to easily construct a query which can be used to retrieve data from a GeoWave datastore.
